  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this dose-confirmatory bridging study is to investigate the safety and
      efficacy of rivaroxaban 5 to 10 mg once-daily (od) dosing in the prevention of venous
      thromboembolism (VTE) in Japanese patients undergoing elective total knee replacement (TKR)
      and to confirm the extrapolability of global data to Japanese patients by comparing with data
      from overseas phase III study (RECORD 3 - Study 11356) and phase II studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
